Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.46,0:00:02.44,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Yuriko!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.44,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Muroto-kun?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.94,0:00:12.70,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.29,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.29,0:00:23.46,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Moritani-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.59,0:00:32.80,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.80,0:00:33.51,Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.70,0:02:26.29,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Moritani-san, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.29,0:02:29.17,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I'm okay. It's just a little bump.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.08,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,This is all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.54,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Kotoura-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.17,0:02:37.17,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,You being arrested, the president being attacked,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.17,0:02:39.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Muroto-senpai getting hurt...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.39,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,It's all... It's all my...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.76,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Because I have this power...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.76,0:02:48.14,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Because I have this power that hurts everyone...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.06,0:02:52.98,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,No. It's not my psychic ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.86,0:02:56.40,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I shouldn't even exist.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.99,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.24,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,What exactly do you think you did?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.24,0:03:02.57,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,All of this is the criminal's fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.49,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Even Manabe told you...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.33,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,That's right, Manabe!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.79,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,What is he doing at a time like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.46,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,No! Don't call Manabe-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.46,0:03:13.75,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Are you still dwelling on that fight you guys had?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.75,0:03:14.88,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.54,0:03:18.30,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Even while we were fighting, he still...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.92,Mind Read,Manabe,0,0,0,,Kotoura is a klutz.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.47,Mind Read,,0,0,0,,I hope she doesn't do anything reckless.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.89,Mind Read,Manabe,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.85,Mind Read,,0,0,0,,When I worry about something happening to her, I can't even eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.31,0:03:28.13,Mind Read,Manabe,0,0,0,,Stupid criminal, just get caught already!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.13,0:03:31.06,Mind Read,Manabe,0,0,0,,Then Kotoura won't have to do anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.89,0:03:34.73,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,He's constantly worrying about me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.34,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Even though I've been so selfish...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.78,0:03:38.86,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.19,0:03:41.74,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I can't just rely on him in times like these.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.61,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Kotoura-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.16,0:03:49.45,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, President... Muroto-senpai... Moritani-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.75,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Manabe-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.75,0:03:55.19,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,For God's sake, why are you always so—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.71,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Oh, who is it now?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.42,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Crap! It's my parents!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.76,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.88,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Yeah... What? Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.88,0:04:07.22,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I know that. I'm not a child anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.18,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,What? Pick up miso and soy sauce on my way home?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.75,0:04:15.35,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Don't call me about running stupid little errands like that right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.40,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.25,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Sorry, Kotoura-san—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.36,0:04:26.45,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Seriously, you all need to stop screwing with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.20,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,That's it. I can't take it anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.85,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,This is the park I visited with Tsukino-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.82,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Huh? Kotoura-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.82,0:05:04.45,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.11,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,We've been running into each other a lot lately, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.87,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Tsukino-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.79,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.79,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Wait! You're hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.46,0:05:18.29,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.22,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.52,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,How long is this going to drag on for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.31,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,You won't understand no matter what I say, and I hate you for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.40,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,She hates me, she says...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.69,0:05:47.61,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,I never thought Kotoura would volunteer to use her own ability.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.61,0:05:51.53,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,But that could put her in danger.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.54,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,What should I have done?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.08,0:05:58.87,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Jeez, who is it at this time of night?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.46,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Shut up! Nobody's home now!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.46,0:06:05.38,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Keep it down! What time do you think—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.38,0:06:06.80,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.59,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Demon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.85,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Sorry it's such a mess, but come on in.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.68,0:06:16.23,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,First, we need to take care of that leg.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.23,0:06:17.73,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Oh... Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.94,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Okay, that should do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.03,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.40,0:06:33.91,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,No police officer would turn a blind eye to an injured girl crying outside alone at night.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.58,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Okay, shall we have some dinner?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.25,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Sit tight, and I'll whip something up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.79,0:06:46.00,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Oh, I should text Moritani-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.55,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.23,0:06:52.59,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm at Tsukino-san's apartment. Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.31,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,And I'm sorry for just taking off.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.09,0:06:57.93,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Send.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.68,0:06:59.85,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.31,0:07:04.82,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.68,0:07:09.24,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I'm a terrible cook...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.61,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Um... Shall I make something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.41,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,You can cook? Seriously?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.47,0:07:20.46,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,U-Um, just where are you planning on beating me?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.83,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,This is so nostalgic...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.83,0:07:27.42,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Even though it's only been three years since we graduated from this grade school.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.13,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Y-You're going to beat me here?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.26,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,The attacker assaulted the club president.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.14,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.67,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She's okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.03,0:07:40.64,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Muroto-senpai protected her, but he didn't suffer any serious injuries either.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.62,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Oh... That's a relief...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.19,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Wait! What about Kotoura? And are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.19,0:07:49.59,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.11,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,So is Kotoura-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.11,0:07:54.49,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,You should've told me that first!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.03,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,But Kotoura-san has disappeared again.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.29,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Me getting arrested,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.91,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,the president being attacked,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.91,0:08:07.34,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,and Muroto-senpai getting hurt, she felt responsible for them all.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.34,0:08:09.80,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Damn, she's talking like that again?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.26,0:08:13.26,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,How much responsibility does that idiot have to force on herself before she's satisfied?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.59,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.59,0:08:19.18,Main,,0,0,0,,You were the one who told me that she was that kind of person.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.56,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,She never told me anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.18,0:08:25.15,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,She kept it all bottled up inside of her.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.27,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.27,0:08:30.21,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Why the hell are you moping around alone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.21,0:08:32.48,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Ow! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.48,0:08:33.86,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,That's my line!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.53,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Why weren't you by Kotoura-san's side?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.66,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Why did you leave her over a little argument?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.62,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,It's true that she can be a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.06,0:08:47.11,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why you should have just stayed with her, regardless of what happened.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.46,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,That would have been enough for her!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.92,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.68,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,No matter what happens, I won't leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.59,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.59,0:09:01.47,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,How could I have forgotten something so obvious until now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.10,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Hey, Manabe, can I tell you something?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.10,0:09:04.85,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.23,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Cut it out. This is no time to be joking ar—
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.57,0:09:09.44,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I love you, Manabe.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.45,0:09:20.62,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I've always, always loved you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.97,0:09:27.96,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Sorry. I love Kotoura.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.92,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,I can't reciprocate your feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.17,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.71,0:09:39.43,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Aww, I got rejected.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.80,0:09:41.60,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,This might sound weird after I confessed to you,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.60,0:09:46.37,Main,Moritai,0,0,0,,but I love you and Kotoura-san being together.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.98,0:09:49.15,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I love watching you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.65,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Moritani...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.61,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Even when you two were fighting,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.61,0:09:56.36,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,instead of seeing it as my chance, I was just worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.57,0:09:58.95,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.95,0:10:02.49,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,But it bothers me when you two aren't together.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.08,0:10:03.86,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.12,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Go after her right now!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.33,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Wait, where exactly is Kotoura?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.92,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't know!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.38,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Why don't you find her yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.05,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.05,0:10:15.77,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.47,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Moritani.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.47,0:10:19.05,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.72,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,When you were bullying Kotoura...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.47,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,Your mind is so disgusting, it made Kotoura puke.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.78,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.52,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,I've felt bad about it ever since.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.52,0:10:31.52,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Why are you bringing that up now?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.52,0:10:34.27,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,You've said far worse things since then.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.27,0:10:35.44,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Like that time you called me a bug.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.82,0:10:36.74,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.95,0:10:50.71,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Well, enough being mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.04,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I guess I'll forward Kotoura-san's text to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.17,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,So your family owns a dojo?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.76,Main Italic,Moritani,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.05,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,Wow! That's so cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.76,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Huh? Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.42,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,I knew from the start that it...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.41,0:11:10.02,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,that it would turn out this way...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.32,0:11:19.24,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Muroto-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.06,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Huh, have you been crying?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.29,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.41,0:11:30.16,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Good. Looks like you're okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.46,0:11:33.32,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Good, nothing! Why did you have to go and...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.00,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Sorry. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.63,0:11:39.27,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,And not just you...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.71,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,If anything had gone wrong, \NKotoura-chan and Moritani-san
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.24,0:11:46.97,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,might have become victims of my selfish quest for revenge, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.64,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I was scared...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.07,0:11:52.56,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I thought you would never open your eyes again.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.06,0:11:57.69,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I thought you would leave me like my mother did...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.06,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Don't do that again!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.49,0:12:05.12,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I never want to see you get hurt because of me again!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.66,Main Italic,Kid,0,0,0,,My mom said a liar's kid will also be a liar!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.21,Main Italic,Kid,0,0,0,,Don't come to school again!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.12,Main Italic,Muroto,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.54,Main Italic,Kid,0,0,0,,You again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.83,0:12:16.96,Main Italic,Kid,0,0,0,,You're a real pain, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.39,0:12:24.55,Main Italic,Kid,0,0,0,,H-Hey, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.31,0:12:31.70,Main Italic,Muroto,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Mifune-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.19,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.48,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Telling me that only makes things harder.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.94,0:12:40.19,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,If I was in that situation again, \NI'd probably do the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.19,0:12:42.61,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,You've always been like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.61,0:12:46.11,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Why do you stay by my side, \Neven when you end up like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.28,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Because I'm Mifune Chizuru's daughter?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.66,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,It's true that I respect Mifune-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.19,0:12:54.92,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,But if I had to choose between you and her, I'd choose you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.50,0:12:57.21,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.92,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,I'm saying {\i1}you're{\i0} more important to me than Mifune-sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.80,0:13:08.64,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,I won't tell you to forget about your anger, or your revenge.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.97,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,But I don't want you to sacrifice the time you have now for that.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.27,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Now...?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.62,0:13:15.18,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.73,0:13:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,You look so happy when you're with Kotoura-kun and the others.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.50,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Like you've forgotten about all the things burdening you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.17,0:13:27.24,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,But... I've always wanted to avenge my mother...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.78,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,I'm on this boat now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll stay with you until the end.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.41,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Even through your selfishness and your lousy bad-guy act.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.67,0:13:38.58,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,What do you mean, lousy act?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.14,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes to accomplish my goals...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.67,0:13:45.67,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,That's the kind of person I am...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.31,0:13:53.39,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Ah, Kotoura-san, please marry me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.43,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'll have to pass on that...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.60,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Aww, too bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.65,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've finished eating.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.19,0:14:05.28,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Is it true that the criminal knew your club president's name?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.82,0:14:06.61,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.49,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.74,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,All right. I'll talk to Yama-san tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.25,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,You can stay here tonight.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.12,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,But wouldn't that be an inconvenience for you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.62,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,What did I tell you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.00,Main,,0,0,0,,No police officer would turn a blind eye to this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.71,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Thank you. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.76,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Sorry for the mess.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.89,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I rarely have anyone over.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.81,0:14:38.14,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Despite my large stature, I've always been pretty timid.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.14,0:14:39.94,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Growing up, I was often the subject of bullying.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.48,0:14:44.98,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I got so tired of it, I began training, and became really strong...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.57,0:14:49.40,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,But that just scared people off, so I remained alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.20,0:14:54.41,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Then, the next thing I knew, I was using my physique to forge myself a career as a detective.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.83,0:14:58.08,Thoughts,Haruka,0,0,0,,She sounds a little like me...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.71,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,But you're lucky, Kotoura-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.12,0:15:03.92,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Even with that power of yours, you've got some great friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.31,0:15:08.59,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll take care of the cleaning up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.34,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,You just make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.85,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.97,0:15:16.60,Thoughts,Haruka,0,0,0,,She's a little ditzy, but she's not a bad person.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.22,0:15:20.35,Thoughts,Haruka,0,0,0,,Still... I feel a little bad for her...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.10,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Something seems off.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.61,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Off? {lol CR, if you use off here you have use off on the sentence above here as well xD} {Was thinking the exact same thing}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.07,0:15:27.53,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,The area where we encountered the attacker.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.95,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,The detective had warned us not to go there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.07,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,What's so strange about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.33,0:15:36.45,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,When you're told not to go somewhere, you naturally become compelled to go there.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.45,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Well, sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.62,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,And one other thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.52,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,The criminal knew you,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.98,0:15:44.46,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,and knew we would go to that location.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.38,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,The only person that could be...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.88,0:15:50.47,Main Italic,Yuriko,0,0,0,,The daughter of Mifune Chizuru.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.05,0:15:53.68,Main Italic,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,I see... The clairvoyant's daughter...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.47,Main Italic,Moritani,0,0,0,,What did the detective want?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.64,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,She said the 2nd Street alley is dangerous, so we should stay away.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.64,0:16:07.73,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,The text that Moritani-san forwarded to me earlier said Kotoura-chan is at that detective's place...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.11,0:16:08.86,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,Yuriko!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.88,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Oh, my phone...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.03,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Huh? It's gone...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.66,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,When did it get there?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.88,0:16:24.75,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Darn, I missed.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.17,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Tsukino-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.34,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,No... Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.67,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Come on, don't give me that look.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.88,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,You've been looking for me all this time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.01,0:16:37.89,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,You mean, you're...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.31,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,That's right! I'm the attacker!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.06,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Looking at you makes me sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.11,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,That mind reading is a real nuisance.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.11,0:16:49.86,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.20,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.49,0:16:56.32,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,You think you can get away?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.70,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.50,Thoughts,Haruka,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on anymore...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.21,0:17:06.42,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I bet people call you a klutz, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.88,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,What kind of an idiot tries to escape by going up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.50,0:17:12.67,Thoughts,Haruka,0,0,0,,President! Muroto-senpai! Moritani-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.51,Mind Read,Haruka,0,0,0,,Manabe-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.84,0:17:17.84,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Kotoura?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.89,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Did something happen, Manabe-kun?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.37,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.37,0:17:23.98,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,More importantly, haven't you found that detective's address yet?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.58,0:17:28.83,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,The police said they won't tell us because it's too dangerous, so Muroto-kun is looking for it now.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hang tight!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.32,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.40,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do if we're too late?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.24,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Where are you, Kotoura?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.12,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.75,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Why did you attack those people?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.49,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Why would you want to hurt anyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.67,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,To relieve stress.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.70,0:17:53.34,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,When you were talking to that woman earlier,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.34,0:17:56.97,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,didn't you wonder why she was laughing all the time?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.53,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,She's always been a spineless coward.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.53,0:18:04.77,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,She crammed all her negative thoughts deep inside her heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.26,0:18:08.23,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,And that's how I came to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.61,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Jealous of their happiness,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.71,Main,,0,0,0,,spiteful because they have friends...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.71,0:18:17.50,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,She wants to ruin the lives of people who have what she doesn't.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.36,0:18:23.08,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Especially those people who remind her of her most painful days, back when she was a student.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.87,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Tsukino-san was that...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.18,0:18:32.50,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,So all this time, I've been burning off the stress that she didn't even know she'd built up over all these years.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.38,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,It was going well until today.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.88,0:18:40.30,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd be backed into a corner by a monster like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.68,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Oh, did that hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.68,0:18:47.68,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,But someone who reads the minds of others can only be described as a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.68,0:18:49.14,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,No! Stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.90,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.04,Main,,0,0,0,,She envied you, even as she wore a smile on her face.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.44,0:18:56.23,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Guess I can't blame her.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.23,0:19:00.49,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,A monster who has everything that she doesn't?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.95,0:19:05.37,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Well, I honestly couldn't care less about her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.77,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I'm just here to have a good time.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.67,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,But I'd rather not get caught, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.04,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.74,0:19:17.22,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,Until recently,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.59,Main Italic,,0,0,0,,I thought the world would be better off if I'd never been born.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.80,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,Sometimes I even felt like I should die.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.34,0:19:26.10,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.76,0:19:29.73,Main Italic,Manabe,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.52,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,I don't want to die! I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.86,Main Italic,Haruka,0,0,0,,I want to live! I want to live!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.82,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Manabe-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.53,0:19:39.28,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Y-You?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.45,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Kotoura.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.74,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Manabe-kun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.74,0:19:47.74,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.37,0:19:51.16,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Sorry. I promised, didn't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.82,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,That I'd always stay with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.18,0:19:54.54,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Manabe-kun...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.60,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Oh, to hell with this!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.60,0:19:58.30,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,If this is how it's gonna be, then you can both...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.13,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Tsukino-san, stop this!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.93,0:20:04.97,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Maybe I am a monster.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.26,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,But I met people who reached out to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.26,0:20:09.89,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No one ever did that for her, and no one ever will!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.65,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,That's what I thought too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.52,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.90,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I'm sure there are people who'll stay with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.40,0:20:22.95,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,So don't give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.95,0:20:23.82,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Kotoura!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.12,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.29,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,She's just a kid playing around!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.46,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,I can hear your voice, Tsukino-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.96,0:20:38.17,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,It's okay. Even I was able to change.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.55,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,If you leave it at this, you'll just be a criminal!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.82,0:20:45.96,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I'll keep helping you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.96,0:20:48.55,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,So stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.85,0:20:51.76,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.11,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Sorry to scare you like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.40,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Tsukino-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.14,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Kotoura-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.14,0:21:09.03,Main,Yuriko,0,0,0,,Kotoura-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.49,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.49,0:21:11.49,Main,Muroto,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.86,0:21:13.45,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Yeah, somehow.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.50,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Wait, Tsukino-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.67,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,I have to pay for my crimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.30,0:21:23.59,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Tsukino-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.47,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.14,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Let's go. Get in the car.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.23,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Yama-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.69,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,When you get out, stop by anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.06,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,I'll treat you to dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.84,Main,Tsukino,0,0,0,,Extra large, right?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.84,0:21:42.15,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,Idiot! You know you're only getting regular!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.32,Main,Manabe,0,0,0,,Kotoura, let's head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.16,0:21:49.45,Main,Moritani,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.49,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.41,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Everyone gather!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:28.41,0:23:29.77,Main,All,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.02,0:23:31.34,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,We've made it to the last episode,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.65,0:23:33.39,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,so let's do the last one together!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.60,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.77,Main,All,0,0,0,,Kotoura-san will live on in perversion forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.77,0:23:41.02,Main,Haruka,0,0,0,,Nooooo!
